information: HERBAMMS, the aromatic herbs and market gardening specialist based in the Pyrénées-Atlantiques, is a company with a growing area of over 45 hectares in France, backed up by some 200 hectares of cooperatives and land in Morocco and Spain that produce aromatic and medicinal herbs and sun-loving fruit and vegetables. Our aromatic herb farms are sited in France and abroad, which enables us to develop a range of very beneficial products. Our fruit is imported from Spain and Morocco to offer you better quality. Lastly, our vegetables are grown in France, which enables us to operate as a wholesaler and distributor.
